s/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果您仲係當緊兵既 我勸您都係早d抽身<br />\n佢地係唔會揀個兵仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做兵賤過地底泥，係冇尊嚴既存在；<br />\n狠心一刀切係對自己最好，越拖就越痛苦。im so proud of you, sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家冇服兵役，只係諗返以前，有感而發姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a7faf26a67d6e5abc24f03d72e5bb942f80622","tid":284628,"uid":13637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做兵仔真係好低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同道中人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾經係 <br />\n但有次佢突然約我個日下午出去 <br />\n我推哂所有野留時間比佢 plan埋去邊度行食乜野<br />\n然後佢係約定時間前半個鐘話唔想出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個日我就直接狠心d block哂佢Whatsapp facebook<br />\ndel埋手機no. 連backup 都del 埋<br />\n掉哂所有同佢有關既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果您仲係當緊兵既 我勸您都係早d抽身<br />\n佢地係唔會揀個兵仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做兵賤過地底泥，係冇尊嚴既存在；<br />\n狠心一刀切係對自己最好，越拖就越痛苦。im so proud of you, sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家冇服兵役，只係諗返以前，有感而發姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過去就由佢過去啦 有幾多人冇試過當兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後搵到個好既就唔會care 自己以前架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}